Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: JD Vance
email: contact@support.donaldjtrump.com
subject: Can I trust you to keep this confidential?
body: I just stepped off stage and I’ve got some troubling news. I’ll always keepit real with you, straight from the heart, just like folks back home would. Ijust stepped off the stage in North Carolina and my team gave me sometroubling news. Kamala is shelling out HUNDREDS OF MILLIONS in a last-ditcheffort to seize back momentum. She’s cashing checks left and right from theHollywood “elites” and corrupt special interests while you read this email.We’re talking about historic spending — with just 4 days until polls open! ButI’ve never been one to run from a fight, and I know you won’t either, Friend.If you join forces with every other PATRIOT in VA by chipping in just $10,we’ll have more than enough to take this fight all the way back to the WhiteHouse! >> GIVE $10 When you support President Trump, you aren’t throwingmoney at a Washington Elitist who only cares about themselves. You’reinvesting in your life, your family’s life, and the life of every Americanpatriot. So if you have just a few bucks to spare, please consider chipping inbefore we face the final FEC deadline of our entire campaign. >> GIVE $10 Ialso really hope you will pledge to donate again before the polls close. Itwould mean the world to me if you could pledge to give again. If you can’t,don’t sweat it and make sure you uncheck the first box. Thank you and Godbless you, JD Vance GIVE $10 Contributions to Trump National Committee JFCare not deductible for federal income tax purposes. All contributions aresubject to the limits and prohibitions of the Federal Election Campaign Act.Contributions from corporations, foreign nationals (i.e., without "greencards"), federal government contractors, and other federally impermissiblesources are strictly prohibited. Contributions made in the name of, orrefunded by, any other person are unlawful. Paid for by Trump NationalCommittee JFC, Inc., a joint fundraising committee composed of and authorizedby Donald J. Trump for President 2024, Inc. and the Republican NationalCommittee. You are receiving this email at dpwillis67@gmail.com Trump NationalCommittee JFC, PO Box 509, Arlington, VA 22216 donaldjtrump.com Thank you forjoining Team Trump. We believe this is an important way to reach ourgrassroots supporters with the most up-to-date information regarding PresidentTrump, and we're glad you're on our team. It's because of grassrootssupporters like YOU that we've been able to consistently call out the FakeNews media EVERY SINGLE TIME they've tried to spread misinformation oroutright LIES about the important work President Trump is doing to SAVEAMERICA. Reaching grassroots supporters directly is CRITICAL if we're going toSave America from the Left. But in order to do that, we need to providesupporters with the most up-to-date information on all of our efforts. TEXT"TRUMP" to 88022 to start receiving text messages from President Trump. It'sbecause of the commitment and support from real Patriots, like YOU, that wewill SAVE AMERICA! Thank you again for your generous support.
